data.oai_dc:dc: 12 Fundus image sequences recorded in 12 young (age 22-31) healthy subjects with a scanning laser ophthalmoscope under near-infrared illumination. Sequences of 5.0 to 5.5 s length, collected at 9 images/s, resulting in 45 to 50 images trimmed to vertical bands (386 x 768 pixels) centered on optic nerve head. Data provided as zipped uncompressed TIFF stacks files
